	* textdomain.c: Protect inclusion of stdlib.h and string.h.

	* loadmsgcat.c: Protect inclusion of stdlib.h.

	* libgettext.h: Protect inclusion of locale.h.
	Allow use in C++ programs.
	Define NULL is not happened already.

